        "char_start": 5,
        "episode_id": "e1743bda-76ff-5586-9e39-3fa45e41ef9a",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-01",
        "text": "Welcome back to Frame & Light. Today we're talking about lighting design, and I'm joined by Daniel Olufemi, commercial lighting director. Daniel Olufemi, thanks for being here.",
        "timestamp_end_ms": 6000,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 0,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/p04_e03.txt"
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    },
    {
      "id": "person:speaker-02",
      "properties": {
        "name": "Daniel Olufemi"
      },
      "type": "Person"
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:2c0efcfbe2283edc",
      "properties": {
        "char_end": 228,
        "char_start": 198,
        "episode_id": "e1743bda-76ff-5586-9e39-3fa45e41ef9a",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-02",
        "text": "Thanks, Leo. Great to be back.",
        "timestamp_end_ms": 12000,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 6000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/p04_e03.txt"
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:af783b261fdc953d",
      "properties": {
        "char_end": 386,
        "char_start": 234,
        "episode_id": "e1743bda-76ff-5586-9e39-3fa45e41ef9a",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-01",
        "text": "This episode is brought to you by Adobe. Adobe Creative Cloud puts Lightroom, Photoshop, and Premiere on every device. Get started at adobe.com/podcast.",
        "timestamp_end_ms": 18000,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 12000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/p04_e03.txt"
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:f61ed165429330ce",
      "properties": {
        "char_end": 490,
        "char_start": 386,
        "episode_id": "e1743bda-76ff-5586-9e39-3fa45e41ef9a",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-01",
        "text": "Walk me through a concrete example. What's something you used to believe about this that you've revised?",
        "timestamp_end_ms": 24000,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 18000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/p04_e03.txt"
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:18217a213026edcb",
      "properties": {
        "char_end": 723,
        "char_start": 507,
        "episode_id": "e1743bda-76ff-5586-9e39-3fa45e41ef9a",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-02",
        "text": "Here's how I think about it. On location, the first decision is always: am I shaping the existing light? We've seen this play out at teams using Adobe. Once you internalize that, the rest of the decisions get easier.",
        "timestamp_end_ms": 30000,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 24000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/p04_e03.txt"
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:a77ea824848f5d67",
      "properties": {
        "char_end": 793,
        "char_start": 729,
        "episode_id": "e1743bda-76ff-5586-9e39-3fa45e41ef9a",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-01",
        "text": "That's a useful framing. How does Profoto fit into this picture?",
        "timestamp_end_ms": 36000,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 30000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/p04_e03.txt"
      },
